    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she's a total stunner. This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied it from day one, keeping it garage-kept, spotless, and up-to-date on everything. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously maintained, you\u2019ve found it! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have, so don't be shy!",
