    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of the A80 chassis. This vehicle features the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six, maintaining factory-spec compression and a pristine sequential turbocharger array with zero shaft play. Power is delivered through the original Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, providing the precise mechanical feedback synonymous with the Golden Era of JDM engineering. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight with all original bushings intact, and the undercarriage shows no signs of thermal stress or oxidation. Every VIN-matched panel and factory seal is preserved, ensuring structural rigidity and peak aerodynamic efficiency. This is a rare, bone-stock specimen optimized for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and analog purity.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
