    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-quality 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman. Finished in a deep, lustrous Midnight Blue Metallic, the exterior is entirely free of stone chips or blemishes, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that yields a mirror-like finish. Inside, the Agate Grey leather remains supple and taut, with absolutely no wear on the seat bolsters and a cabin that retains its original factory scent. Every switch operates with tactile precision, and the infotainment display is flawless. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships and kept in a climate-controlled garage. With exceptionally low mileage and a comprehensive service history, this is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
